                        <i class="icon-stack4"></i> Revision

                            <a rel="nofollow" href="#">
                                C,D

                <p>We have decided to add comments to facilitate communication and interaction between FUTBIN users. We believe and hope that we can build a stable community in FUTBIN and that comments will be a part of it. We have created a guideline, which will help you to understand how to use our comments system.</p>
                <h6 class="text-success">Do's:</h6>
                <ul>
                    <li>Comment your opinion on things, and/or add valuable information</li>
                    <li>Reply to other comments in a respectful manner</li>
                    <li>Report comments which are offensive</li>
                </ul>

                <h6 class="text-danger">Don'ts</h6>
                <ul>
                    <li>Use any racism</li>
                    <li>Attack or threat other users. It's ok to disagree with others, but keep the comments polite and respectful</li>
                    <li>Spam or post spam content</li>
                    <li>Link other websites</li>
                </ul>

                    Violation of the above rules can lead to account closure.
                </div>
